        "# Observation\n",
        "\n",
        "1. One-time customers dominate\n",
        "93,099 out of 96,096 customers placed exactly one order.\n",
        "- 96.9% of customer base\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "2. Repeat purchasing is rare\n",
