        "  Only 2,997 customers\n",
        "  placed more than one order.\n",
        "  - 3.1%\n",
        "\n",
        "3. Repeat customers are mostly \"2-order customers\"\n",
        "\n",
        "Among repeat customers 2,745 out of 2,997 placed exactly 2 orders.\n",
        "- 91.6%\n",
        "\n",
        "4. Highly loyal customers are extremely rare\n",
        "\n",
        "49 customers placed 4 or more orders.\n",
        "And only 1 customer placed 17 orders.\n",
